msgid "Welcome to Duka Mwecheche!"
msgstr "Ũkaribũ Kũ Duka Mwecheche!"

msgid "This quick tutorial will guide you through the key features of your dashboard. You can always replay it from the menu under your username."
msgstr "Mũrutani ũno wa haraka nĩũkũlongoria kũhuhũka maũndũ ma mũsingi ma dashibodi yaku. Ũngĩwurora tena ihinda o na rĩngĩ kuuma menũ ya nthĩ ya rĩĩtwa rĩaku."

msgid "Your Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashibodi Yaku"

msgid "Your <strong>Supplier Dashboard</strong> shows key stats: active clients, pending bids, won bids, and open procurement requests."
msgstr "<strong>Dashibodi ya Mũheani</strong> yaku ĩonesya takwimu cia mũsingi: ateja arĩ mbere, mabĩdi ĩkĩethĩire, mabĩdi amacĩhĩtĩtwo, na maũhĩro ma ũgũrani matwĩkĩte."

msgid "Click <strong>Browse Requests</strong> to find procurement opportunities from businesses. Submit competitive bids to win supply contracts."
msgstr "Finya <strong>Rora Maũhĩro</strong> gũnenga mawĩra ya ũgũrani kuuma maciarwa. Tũma mabĩdi ya ũgwĩtana gũcĩhĩtia mikataba ya ũheani."

msgid "Track Your Bids"
msgstr "Taara Mabĩdi Mako"

msgid "Under <strong>My Bids</strong>, monitor the status of all your bid submissions — pending, awarded, or rejected."
msgstr "Nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Mabĩdi Makwa</strong>, taara hali ya mabĩdi mako mothe ĩhĩtwo — ĩkĩethĩire, amacĩhĩtĩtwo, kana akanĩtwo."

msgid "Connect with Businesses"
msgstr "Hũrĩrana na Maciarwa"

msgid "Use <strong>Browse Businesses</strong> to discover potential clients. Apply to become their approved supplier."
msgstr "Thĩmia <strong>Rora Maciarwa</strong> gũnenga ateja ala makĩhĩtĩko. Hĩra wĩ mũheani wao ũkwĩtĩkĩtwo."

msgid "Client Relationships"
msgstr "Ũhũrĩrano na Ateja"

msgid "Once approved, view your client list under <strong>My Clients</strong>. Build strong relationships for repeat procurement."
msgstr "Ũkĩkwĩtĩkĩtwo, rora mũkusayo wa ateja waku nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Ateja Akwa</strong>. Tung'a ũhũrĩrano wa nguvu kũrĩ ũgũrani wĩũke."

msgid "You're All Set!"
msgstr "Ũhaarĩire Wega!"

msgid "Start browsing procurement requests to grow your supply network! Replay this tutorial from your username menu anytime."
msgstr "Ambĩrĩria kurora maũhĩro ma ũgũrani gũkua mũnyororo waku wa ũheani! Urora mũrutani ũno tena kuuma menũ ya rĩĩtwa rĩaku ihinda o na rĩngĩ."

msgid "Your <strong>Rider Dashboard</strong> shows active deliveries, completed orders, and your performance score."
msgstr "<strong>Dashibodi ya Mũtwarĩ wa Boda</strong> yaku ĩonesya ũheanio ĩrĩ mbere, maodha ĩmalĩire, na alama yaku ya utendaji."

msgid "Availability Toggle"
msgstr "Garũra Ũkwatĩkana"

msgid "Toggle your <strong>availability</strong> status so businesses know when you are ready to accept deliveries."
msgstr "Garũra hali yaku ya <strong>ũkwatĩkana</strong> nĩguo maciarwa maĩve ihinda ũkwĩhaarĩiria gũkĩria ũheanio."

msgid "View your current delivery assignments under <strong>Active Deliveries</strong>. See customer details, location, and order amounts."
msgstr "Rora mĩvango yaku ya ũheanio ya hĩnĩ nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Ũheanio Ĩrĩ Mbere</strong>. Ona ũhoro wa mteja, kũrĩa, na wingi wa odha."

msgid "Check <strong>Delivery History</strong> for a complete record of all your past deliveries."
msgstr "Angalia <strong>Ũhoro wa Ũheanio</strong> kũrĩ rekodi ya ũhoro wothe wa ũheanio wako wa tene."

msgid "Track your total earnings and delivery count under <strong>My Earnings</strong>."
msgstr "Taara mapato mako mothe na wingi wa ũheanio nthĩinĩ wa <strong>Mapato Makwa</strong>."

msgid "Stay available to receive delivery assignments! Replay this tutorial from your username menu anytime."
msgstr "Ikala ũkwatĩkana gũkĩria mĩvango ya ũheanio! Urora mũrutani ũno tena kuuma menũ ya rĩĩtwa rĩaku ihinda o na rĩngĩ."

