msgid "Inventory Management"
msgstr "Ũtaari wa Hisa"

msgid "Track stock levels, costs, and reorder points in real time. Never run out of stock again."
msgstr "Taara kĩhingo kĩa hisa, ngeca, na kĩhingo kĩa gũrũra ĩsaa rĩrĩa rĩa. Ũtigwe hisa gĩthũ."

msgid "Online Marketplace"
msgstr "Soko Online"

msgid "Your own storefront where customers browse and order directly. No middleman."
msgstr "Nduka yaku cio cio ĩrĩa ateja tambera na odha thĩinĩ. Gũtĩkorwo na mũhũthĩrĩri."

msgid "M-Pesa Payments"
msgstr "Marĩba ya M-Pesa"

msgid "Accept payments via Lipa Na M-Pesa. Instant STK Push to your customers' phones."
msgstr "Kĩria marĩba na Lipa Na M-Pesa. STK Push ĩĩngĩira simu cia ateja akwa haraka."

msgid "USSD Access"
msgstr "Ũtũhũka wa USSD"

msgid "Record sales and check stock via USSD. Works on any phone, no internet needed."
msgstr "Andĩka mauzo na angalia hisa na USSD. Ĩgakĩra simu yothe, ĩtahitĩkie intaneti."

msgid "Analytics Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashibodi ya Takwimu"

msgid "See your top products, revenue trends, and profit margins at a glance."
msgstr "Rora indo ciau nzuri, mwelekeo wa mapato, na faida kwa mũthethanio."

msgid "Staff Management"
msgstr "Ũtaari wa Andũ a Wĩra"

msgid "Add staff, assign roles, and get notified when they log in or record transactions."
msgstr "Ongera andũ a wĩra, hea miima, na ũkĩriwo ĩla arĩkĩa kũtoonya kana gũtagwa mĩciaro."

msgid "Is Duka Mwecheche free?"
msgstr "Duka Mwecheche nĩ ya bũre?"

msgid "Yes! The platform is completely free for all businesses. You only pay standard M-Pesa transaction fees when accepting payments."
msgstr "Ĩĩ! Jukwaa nĩ ya bũre wega kũrĩ maciarwa mothe. Ũrĩbia tũ ngeca cia M-Pesa cia kawaida ĩĩkiria marĩba."

msgid "Do I need a smartphone?"
msgstr "Nĩhĩtĩkĩte simu ya ũhotu?"

msgid "No. You can manage your stock via USSD on any basic phone. The web app works on smartphones and computers too."
msgstr "Aaa. Ũngĩtaara hisa yaku na USSD simu yothe ya kawaida. App ya wavuti ĩgakĩra simu za ũhotu na kompyuta pia."

msgid "How do customers find my shop?"
msgstr "Ateja akwa meheanga nduka yakwa atĩa?"

msgid "Once you register and add items with prices, your business appears on the Marketplace. Customers can search by location and product."
msgstr "Ũkĩandĩkĩsa na ũkĩongera indo na ngeca, biashara yaku ĩonekaga Soko. Ateja mĩngĩtaagia na kũrĩa na kĩndũ."

msgid "Is my data safe?"
msgstr "Data yakwa nĩ hĩ?"

msgid "Absolutely. Your data is stored securely on cloud servers with regular backups. Only you and your staff can access your business data."
msgstr "Ĩĩ na ũhotu wothe. Data yaku ĩhĩthiĩka wega seva cia cloud na nakopi cia mara kwa mara. Nawe o wĩwe na andũ a wĩra akwa nĩo mĩngĩhũka data ya biashara yaku."

msgid "Can I accept M-Pesa payments?"
msgstr "Nĩwĩka kĩria marĩba ya M-Pesa?"

msgid "Yes. We integrate with Safaricom's Daraja API. You'll need a Till or Paybill number from Safaricom to receive funds directly."
msgstr "Ĩĩ. Nĩtũhũrĩrana na API ya Daraja ya Safaricom. Nĩũhĩtĩkie namba ya Till kana Paybill kuuma Safaricom gũkĩria mbeca thĩinĩ."

msgid "How do I add staff?"
msgstr "Nĩongereraga andũ a wĩra atĩa?"

msgid "Go to Manage -> Staff -> Add Staff. Staff members can record transactions but cannot access business settings or financial reports."
msgstr "Enda Taara -> Andũ a Wĩra -> Ongera Mũndũ wa Wĩra. Andũ a wĩra mĩngĩtagwa mĩciaro no mĩtĩũhũka mĩtugo ya biashara kana ripoti cia mbeca."

msgid "No business profile found."
msgstr "Gũtĩkorwo na Wasifu wa Biashara Ĩnongekĩtwo."

